member.remarks:
If you want two (or more) columns to equally share the available free space, set this property to True. If you want this column to have a larger or smaller share of the free space, you must set the FreeSpaceProportion property explicitly.
Space filling columns are still governed by the MinimumWidth and MaximumWidth properties.
///

example.code:
private GenericValueEditor GetColorEditor(Color startColor) {
	GenericValueEditor editor = new GenericValueEditor();
	editor.EditedType = typeof(Color);
	editor.Value = startColor;
	return editor;
}
